intro: When the system fails, the protocol begins.
description:
ULTRASHOT: Kill Protocol plunges you into a collapsing world where each mission takes you deeper into chaos. As a lone operative, you're deployed to eliminate growing threats spreading across hostile zones.

Every level challenges you to push forward, clearing out waves of enemies that become increasingly aggressive and unpredictable. But the real test comes at the end—where a powerful adversary awaits, guarding the path to what’s next.

No one is coming to help. You are the last defense against a force that multiplies with every hour. As the enemy evolves, so must you—adapting, enduring, and executing the mission at all costs.

The protocol has been activated. There’s no turning back.
